metadata.name: Hosta Longissima  Ballerina
metadata.description:
2200x4073 PNG
by KOOka 3/13/2022

The [ Hosta Longissima ] flower meaning is "forgotten love".
You are destined to be used by your loved ones.
It's a vicious cycle of being hurt and sad every time you're broken, but you do the same thing over and over again.
I worked as a ballerina expressing such sadness.
